      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for the feedback. Assembly.v1_0_0 schema defines\n\"Producer\" for the manufacturer.\nDMTF LongDescription: \"shall be equal to the\nManufacturer field value in a PLDM FRU structure\".\nChanged mapping to Asset.Manufacturer -\u003e Producer in PS2.\n\nSee PS2:\nhttps://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/bmcweb/+/88571/1..2/redfish-core/lib/assembly.hpp#159\nhttps://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/bmcweb/+/88571/1..2/docs/Redfish.md#498",
      "parentUuid": "67aba245_8e8eed76",
